{"type":"text","timestamp":1778978848300,"sessionID":"ses_1cc994489ffeFlBi4C0jxCUInA","part":{"id":"prt_e3366ece2001wCpCTJolY4xkiD","messageID":"msg_e3366d742001sqUYtwIcofD5Th","sessionID":"ses_1cc994489ffeFlBi4C0jxCUInA","type":"text","text":"The issue is clear: it asks for xref updates on four catalytic activity terms, one label change, and one definition xref update. I’m checking the existing stanzas and current repo state, then I’ll make the term edits through checkout/checkin rather than editing `go-edit.obo` directly.","time":{"start":1778978843875,"end":1778978848298}}}
